These are Puzzles for 2x2 Level 4

.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-4-1::.
The people have 2 different hobbies: card-games, collecting
There are 2 different nationalities: polish, french
1. the polish is in an even position##4
2. the french is the person who's hobby is collecting##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |     1      |     2      |
| Hobby   | collecting | card-games |
| Nationality     | french    | polish   |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-4-2::.
There 2 different types of food: apricot, raspberry
The people prefer 2 different types of sport: sailing, weightlifting
1. the person who's sport is sailing is in an odd position##4
2. the person eating raspberry is on the left of the person eating apricot##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |    1     |       2       |
| Food   | raspberry | apricot        |
| Sport      | sailing  | weightlifting |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-4-3::.
The people prefer 2 different music-genres: ambient, house
There are 2 different favourite beverages: iced-tea, 7up
1. the person drinking iced-tea is in an odd position##4
2. the fan of house is on the left of the fan of ambient##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |    2    |
| Music-Genre   | house    | ambient |
| Beverage   | iced-tea | 7up |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-4-4::.
