The people prefer 2 different music-genres: metal, house
1. the person drinking lemonade is on the right of the person drinking 7up##1
2. the fan of house is in an even position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|            |    1     |    2     |
| Beverage   | 7up      | lemonade |
| Music-Genre       | metal | house    |

