.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-4-5::.
The people have 2 different jobs:  fisherman, social-worker
House: craftsman, tower
1. the craftsman house is in an even position##4
2. the social-worker is on the right of the fisherman##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |       2       |
| Job           | fisherman | social-worker |
| House   | tower    | craftsman         |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-4-6::.
The people prefer 2 different types of sport: climbing, rugby
City: berlin, london
1. the person traveling to berlin is in an even position##4
2. the person traveling to london is on the left of the person who's sport is climbing##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |   1   |     2     |
| Sport       | rugby | climbing  |
| City   | london  | berlin |

